GTE TELEPHONE STRIKE AVERTED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A threatened strike by 15,000 GTE California employees has been averted with an 
agreement reached Friday evening, a spokeswoman for the telephone company said. 
</P>
<P>
