<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bilzerian Denies Charges: Former Singer Co. Chairman Paul A. Bilzerian denied 
charges made by the SEC in a civil suit filed last week that he has transferred 
assets out of the United States to prevent the government from recovering more 
than $31 million in profit it says he made from an unsuccessful takeover 
