<P>
BILZERIAN, PAUL; SECURITIES FRAUD; UNITED STATES -- SUITS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070889-0084 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 79551 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 8, 1989, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part 4; Page 3; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
