<HEADLINE>
<P>
MOBSTER GENE GOTTI GETS 50-YEAR PRISON SENTENCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Gene Gotti, brother of reputed Gambino mob boss John Gotti, was sentenced 
Friday to 50 years in prison for running a multimillion-dollar drug ring. 
Co-defendant John Carneglia also was given 50 years, and both defendants were 
fined $75,000. 
</P>
