<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOME DESIGN; 
</P>
<P>
A SPECIAL ISSUE OF ORANGE COUNTY LIFE; 
</P>
<P>
NEW PRODUCTS TO AID HOMEOWNERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ANDY LANG, AP Newsfeatures 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
What's new on the market? 
</P>
<P>
A wood glue designed especially for darker woods. 
</P>
<P>
Manufacturer's claim: The super-strength polymer glue is formulated to produce 
a close match to darker wood, such as mahogany, cherry and cedar. It helps to 
eliminate visible seams some yellow wood glues leave behind. It allows for easy 
alignment of parts, good penetration of woods and easy cleanup, yet bonds 
quickly. It is resistant to lacquers, varnishes, water and heat when dry. It 
also resists softening and gumming-up of sandpaper as well as the heat 
generated by sanding and cutting. It is water-based, non-sniffable and without 
harmful fumes. 
</P>
<P>
A solution that plates and replates pure gold over ordinary metals at home. 
</P>
<P>
Manufacturer's claim: The solution is a bath that contains 24-karat gold in 
liquid form and works with the natural electromotive forces within the metals 
themselves. It will plate all jewelry and small items -- whether gold, gold 
plate, silver, silver plate, nickel, brass, copper or bronze -- quickly and 
inexpensively. It adheres evenly to the surface of clean base metals without 
forming ridges or lines. Items are placed in a basket with the activator for 
only 10 to 15 seconds and then washed in soapy water and buffed with a soft 
cloth. 
</P>
<P>
A hand masker-dispenser. 
</P>
<P>
Manufacturer's claim: The dispenser enables professional or amateur painters to 
dispense a continuous sheet of masking paper or film in one smooth stroke. It 
is lightweight and compact. It places the protecting paper in place on walls, 
windows and floors so they are not damaged by paint runs, roller mist or 
overspray. It has only two moving parts and does not need lubrication. It comes 
with a carrying holster for convenience. 
</P>
<P>
The glue is manufactured by Borden Inc., 180 E. Broad St., Columbus, Ohio 
43215; the gold replating solution by Sheffield Plate Polish Co., 1600 
Orrington Ave., Evanston, Ill. 60201 and the masking tape dispenser by 3M DOY 
Business, Building 223-4S-01, 3M Center, St. Paul, Minn. 55144. 
</P>
</TEXT>
